des: "Prepared chopped onions and garlic help get these tasty burgers with Cheddar cheese on the table fast, for a quick lunch or weeknight dinner."
ins:
Combine ground beef and Recipe Ready Chopped Onions, Garlic in medium bowl; shape into 6 patties.
Grill or broil until desired doneness; top with cheese.* Serve on buns with lettuce leaves and, if desired, sliced tomatoes.
